{"parentUuid":"73f8f9af-2b9b-4de5-9477-5f41b574d217","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016abeiAfpRJZCk9BGVv8Aaa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3120,"cache_read_input_tokens":13682,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3120},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"}},"requestId":"req_011CZX3AfhZk2KaXjxWwnQMz","type":"assistant","uuid":"3591ec86-61ca-43b8-ad5b-b84b4f635ff8","timestamp":"2026-03-29T08:14:56.023Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"15d3662e-5aa5-4d76-97db-b1a070911c01","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"enrollment"}
{"parentUuid":"3591ec86-61ca-43b8-ad5b-b84b4f635ff8","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_016abeiAfpRJZCk9BGVv8Aaa","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Go の標準 `net/http` パッケージには**ミドルウェア専用の機能はありません**が、ミドルウェアパターンを実装できます。\n\n## 標準的なミドルウェアの書き方\n\n`http.Handler` インターフェースをラップするだけで実現できます：\n\n```go\n// ミドルウェアの型\ntype Middleware func(http.Handler) http.Handler\n\n// 例: ログミドルウェア\nfunc LoggingMiddleware(next http.Handler) http.Handler {\n    return http.HandlerFunc(func(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request) {\n        log.Printf(\"%s %s\", r.Method, r.URL.Path)\n        next.ServeHTTP(w, r)\n    })\n}\n\n// 適用\nmux := http.NewServeMux()\nmux.HandleFunc(\"/\", handler)\n\nhttp.ListenAndServe(\":8080\", LoggingMiddleware(mux))\n```\n\n## 複数ミドルウェアのチェーン\n\n標準ではチェーン用ヘルパーはないので自作か、軽量ライブラリを使います：\n\n```go\n// 自作チェーン\nfunc Chain(h http.Handler, middlewares ...Middleware) http.Handler {\n    for i := len(middlewares) - 1; i >= 0; i-- {\n        h = middlewares[i](h)\n    }\n    return h\n}\n```\n\n## Go 1.22+ の `net/http`\n\nGo 1.22 で `ServeMux` がパスパラメータ・メソッドマッチングに対応しましたが、ミドルウェア機能は追加されていません。\n\n---\n\n実用上は [chi](https://github.com/go-chi/chi) や [echo](https://echo.labstack.com/) を使うとミドルウェアチェーンが簡単に書けます。このプロジェクトで使っているフレームワークを確認しますか？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3120,"cache_read_input_tokens":13682,"output_tokens":568,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3120,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZX3AfhZk2KaXjxWwnQMz","type":"assistant","uuid":"c06e2f96-3842-472b-bbb1-ed9690be0fbc","timestamp":"2026-03-29T08:15:03.401Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"15d3662e-5aa5-4d76-97db-b1a070911c01","version":"2.1.84